'''''Re:CREATORS''''' (Japanese:'''{{lj|レクリエイターズ}}''') is an anime produced by TROYCA.  The original story is written by Rei Hiroe. 
==Plot==
==Characters==
*Sōta Mizushino (Japanese: {{lj|水篠颯太}})
:CV: Daiki Yamashita
*Selejia Yupitiria (Japanese: {{lj|セレジア・ユピティリア}})
:CV: Mikako Komatsu
