:CV: Inori Minase
*Aristeria February (Japanese: {{lj|アリステリア・フェブラリィ}})
:CV: Yōko Hikasa
*Mamika Kirameki ((Japanese: {{lj|煌樹まみか}})
:CV: Rie Murakawa
*Yūya Mirokuji (Japanese: {{lj|弥勒寺優夜}})
:CV: Kenichi Suzumura
*Rui Kanoya (Japanese: {{lj|鹿屋瑠偉}})
:CV: Sora Amamiya
*Magane Chikujōin (Japanese: {{lj|築城院真鍳}})
:CV: Maaya Sakamoto
*Blitz Tokar (Japanese: {{lj|ブリッツ・トーカー}})
:CV: Atsushi Ono
*Military Uniform Princess (Japanese: {{lj|軍服の姫君}})
:CV: Aki Toyosaki

